description: Vendetta is the big BAD at US right now, after watching her in the test Tag Team Match we think she just looks awesome. However our rankings are based on single match play. When the dust settles will Vendetta be the US champion this year? The Badger would have to agree, as she got decimated on the mat.
title: Vendetta (9-3) Ranked 2nd The Badger (1-1) Ranked 11th
